{"tid":898272,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"真正免費HD墨香11月18號開服","createTime":"2018-11-11T14:33:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T11:36:10.000Z","uid":24461,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"dac891583d22e59e2429914713a392b7dae0c6fa","tid":898272,"uid":24461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T14:33:09.000Z","msg":"真正免費★『HD墨香』★ <br />\n★★18/11/2018 時間:18:00 強勢強費開服!!!<br />\n★★18/11/2018 時間:18:00 強勢強費開服!!!<br />\n★★18/11/2018 時間:18:00 強勢強費開服!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HDmsoADMIN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHDmsoADMIN&d=oFlJJ1StRo6iSXDaT3Iep0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=cd6f2579\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HDmsoADMIN</a><br />\n<br />\n希望閣下能細心閱讀我們開服的理念<br />\n<br />\n這些年來在網上時不時都會聽到一些玩家懷念童年時代的墨香，<br />\n<br />\n有些回憶，朋友甚至戀人都因為當年墨香而認識，甚至直到現在還在<br />\n<br />\n維繫，「2006年」墨香初推出，深受大眾玩家喜愛，但隨著時間的流水<br />\n<br />\n慢慢已經失去原味的墨香了，隨著時代的改變市面上各式各樣的服<br />\n<br />\n都出盡法寶「變態的攻血，音速升級速度，無限的祝福 等等...？」<br />\n<br />\n我並不是要否決這些設定，或是去評擊任何服，因為玩家口味各個不一<br />\n<br />\n想說的是，當看到這樣的情境，而是我更懷念當年的<br />\n<br />\n攤位滿佈長安，壓等，組隊打王怪，用什麼奇招去組合一件裝備，<br />\n<br />\n白狼甲的模樣，密室的忍者，鄭州的羅羅樣子經已很模糊了...。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n『HD墨香』希望可以為大家帶來一個懷念的服，而且是『絕對免費』<br />\n<br />\n什麼是『絕對免費』，商城的符咒卷軸都是透過遊戲幣買<br />\n<br />\n抽獎系統用的是泡點，王怪可得到百寶，材料，符文。<br />\n<br />\n我們希望做一個良心出品的懷舊服，所以設置如下：<br />\n<br />\n經驗１倍<br />\n技能點３倍<br />\n金錢１倍<br />\n掉寶１倍<br />\n武功３倍<br />\n有內掛系統升級<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 免費泡點抽獎!!!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 免費泡點抽獎!!!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 免費泡點抽獎!!!<br />\n<br />\n靠玩家雙手創造出自己的成就，開創古代山河！！<br />\n<br />\n『絕對免費』，只會不定時出一些禮品包/抽獎包，來維持服務器支出<br />\n<br />\n良心出品為的只是希望能懷念過去<br />\n<br />\n永久開服給所有愛墨香的玩家細心回味直到永遠！<br />\n<br />\nFACEBOOK粉絲專頁：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HDmsoADMIN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHDmsoADMIN&d=oFlJJ1StRo6iSXDaT3Iep0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=cd6f2579\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HDmsoADMIN</a>/<br />\n<br />\n微信客服代理(增加後可以進入微信討論群)：<br />\nmsoagent888<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【宣傳】ＨＤ墨香宣傳活動詳情：<br />\n<br />\n　1.　在論壇/FACEBOOK分享以上貼文 <br />\n或在微信/QQ 100人以上墨香群分享<br />\n<br />\n　2.　截圖給FACEBOOK專頁GM ,<br />\n驗證後會發放序號給玩家, 開服進遊戲後玩家可憑序號找GM換領獎品<br />\n <br />\n *每個序號只可使用一次<br />\n*GM每日派發獎勵時間為每日晚上7:00-8:00<br />\n <br />\n活動獎勵:每3個宣傳貼文可獲得宣傳禮包一個, 開啟禮包會獲得豐富禮品（符咒,多福,祝福石,百寶等等稀有物品）<br />\n           <br />\n活動時間:即日起至2018年11月18日6:00"},{"pid":"493dbe19bb2e000abe469233c336fd0671b69aeb","tid":898272,"uid":141871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T14:37:14.000Z","msg":"唔洗課金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1a9a0f4bb11ff2e66c21a07faccb639a753be1","tid":898272,"uid":109086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T14:39:38.000Z","msg":"1倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c19ad737396ae7cffed916455e0f4469e785243f","tid":898272,"uid":191812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T14:45:49.000Z","msg":"墨香<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b63bac4d365b5c4d0a52cfd756b5eb37dae5e19","tid":898272,"uid":9231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T14:51:38.000Z","msg":"只會不定時出一些禮品包/抽獎包<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e20956ba3352cc6a4f33ce3168d7fdb05fae31c","tid":898272,"uid":24461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T04:12:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e41efea317599023e7bbb57aca5e393e4f34368","tid":898272,"uid":673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T04:13:21.000Z","msg":"微信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"407988515a6ec85e5755c02aabd457d3bce19a49","tid":898272,"uid":87154,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T04:25:06.000Z","msg":"每次都係新ac開墨香post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個服係咪長遠都免費<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩家唔需要課金？<img s